</ul>
<ul>
<li>They are smoking crack.
<ul>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="news" id="CITEREFGalli.2C_Peter2003">Galli, Peter (2003-08-20). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.eweek.com/c/a/Past-News/Torvalds-Slams-SCO/">"Torvalds Slams SCO"</a>. eWeek<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2008-03-01</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Torvalds+Slams+SCO&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Galli%2C+Peter&amp;rft.au=Galli%2C+Peter&amp;rft.date=2003-08-20&amp;rft.pub=eWeek&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eweek.com%2Fc%2Fa%2FPast-News%2FTorvalds-Slams-SCO%2F&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Linus_Torvalds"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li>Notes: said about <a href="//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/SCO_Group" class="extiw" title="w:SCO Group">SCO</a>.</li>
