<ul>
<li>Torvalds, Linus (<span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2005-07-31">2005-07-31</span>). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.ussg.iu.edu/hypermail/linux/kernel/0507.3/2331.html">Message</a>. <i>linux-kernel mailing list</i>. IU. Retrieved on 2006-08-28.</li>
