<li>[In response to <a rel="nofollow" class="external autonumber" href="http://www.oregonlive.com/portland/index.ssf/2012/07/northeast_portland_man_who_str.html">[4]</a>] Good job. More public indecency, less TSA, that's what I say.
<ul>
<li>Torvalds, Linus (<span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2012-07-18">2012-07-18</span>). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://plus.google.com/102150693225130002912/posts/1FSzP9J5Qm9">Linus Torvalds - Google+</a>. Retrieved on 2012-07-27.</li>
