<h4><span class="mw-headline" id="Audience_Q.26A_following_interview_panel_at_Aalto_University_Center.2C_2012"><i>Audience Q&amp;A following interview panel at Aalto University Center</i>, 2012</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Linus_Torvalds&amp;action=edit&amp;section=17" title="Edit section: Audience Q&amp;A following interview panel at Aalto University Center, 2012">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h4>
