<li>Microsoft isn't evil, they just make really crappy operating systems.
<ul>
<li>Torvalds, Linus (<span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2013-01-29">2013-01-29</span>). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://twitter.com/linus__torvalds/status/296333371393597440">Linus Torvalds on Twitter</a>. Retrieved on 2016-07-26.</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>But this is definitely another of those "This is our most desperate hour. Help me, Al-biwan Ke-Viro, you're my only hope" issues. Al? Please don't make me wear that golden bikini.
<ul>
<li>Torvalds, Linus (<span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2013-03-07">2013-03-07</span>). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://article.gmane.org/gmane.linux.kernel/1453069">Re: fasync_remove_entry oops</a>. Retrieved on 2013-05-01.</li>
