</li>
<li>I hope I won't end up having to hunt you all down and kill you in your sleep.
<ul>
<li>Torvalds, Linus (<span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2013-04-05">2013-04-05</span>). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://plus.google.com/102150693225130002912/posts/hvnMn1fFKEm">Linus Torvalds - Google+</a>. Retrieved on 2013-04-05.</li>
